<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> kō-vicai
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ya-nantiv<unclear>i</unclear>kkirama
<lb n="3" break="no"/>parumaṟku yā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṇṭu mūṉṟ-ā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vatu Ūṟṟukkā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṭṭu-<unclear>k</unclear>kōṭṭa<unclear>t</unclear>tu
<lb n="7" break="no"/><unclear>p</unclear> perumpālai
<lb n="8"/>Ūrt tiruppālai
<lb n="9" break="no"/>y-ūr kiḻavaṉṉ aṭa
<lb n="10" break="no"/>vi śrīkaṅkaraiyar
<lb n="11"/>nērkuṭṭi perumāṉā
